reviewText:
Program content is fine, but as of today, it states that Japanese is a language option for this DVD set. However, the only language available on this set is English.

Disappointed that the original Japanese has been removed and that the product description was incorrect.
this is a great collection of pokemon episodes. it is fun and enjoyable to watch. if you have not seen this dvd set then I recommend you do

Got this box set for my 5 year old daughter as a Christmas gift. She really enjoyed it, as a matter of fact she watched every disc in 24 hours. It was Christmas school vacation so I let her as a special treat! Good choice for the little Pokemon fans out there.
Good collection
thanks
I love this Pokmon movie its the best.
You can't go wrong with Pokemon.  I am a parent, and even I find them witty and entertaining.  I find Pikachu adorable.

Im still a huge Pokemon fan , so I still purchase Pokemon products from the figures to the show and movies . Dont have any of the games so I mainly stay to the series and figure line of Pokemon and all their products are well made and amazing . Its Pokemon , its funa and still Lovable .

Love Dawn shes one of my favorite characters so far that join Ash in his adventures .
this anime is very  good and it is recomended to other kids or other people who enjoy pokemon.  this anime is also exciting.
I have enjoyed the Pokmon series since its debut in 1998! This is another great addition to my Pokmon DVD collection! :) The DVDs arrived in great condition and was shipped very quickly!
I chose this highest rating as my kiddo said this was exacty the episodes he wanted to see - would buy more when they come out.

I bought this for my kids and they loved it. The are 15 and 7 and this collection is one thing they can sit down together and watch without a fight. I love it too and it arrived intact and in excellent working order. I would recommend this to everyone.

I love it. A great season indeed. I love the new characters' like Dawn, Zoey, Piplup, Paul, Professor Rowan, Chimchar, Turtwig, etc. Funny in some ways, some ways in not. My other favorite series are "Save Me Lollipop.","Kodocha.","Negima! Magister Negi Magi.", "Love Hina.","Dragon Ball.","Dragon Ball Z.", "Bakugan Battle Brawlers.","Digimon Digital Monsters.", and most of all "Code Lyoko." If you're an anime fan I reccomend all these great series. I totally give this season five stars.

Like all pokemon movies and series, this one is cute and fun to watch with people of all ages. I always like the bonds they have with the pokemon, and those that they catch along the way. Great Product for all ages!
Love it
